item.title: CVE-2022-3920|2024-08-03T01:20:58.854Z -- hashicorp -- consul
item.description: HashiCorp Consul and Consul Enterprise 1.13.0 up to 1.13.3 do not filter cluster filtering's imported nodes and services for HTTP or RPC endpoints used by the UI. Fixed in 1.14.0.
